#Pcd token definition please refer to the following link:
#https://confluence.cixtech.com/display/SW/SKY1+uefi+PCD+Token+definition
#----------------------------------------------------------------
#           Pcd token definition
#----------------------------------------------------------------
# domain	    PCD Token range	       count
# CPU	        0x00000001 ~ 0x00000080 128
# FCH	        0x00000081 ~ 0x00000100	128
# I2C     	  0x00000101 ~ 0x00000140	64
# SPI	        0x00000141 ~ 0x00000180	64
# pinmux/gpio	0x00000181 ~0x000001C0	64
# memlayout	  0x000001C1 ~0x00000200	64

# PCIE	      0x00000201 ~ 0x00000280	128
# GMAC	      0x00000281 ~ 0x00000300	128
# USB	        0x00000301 ~ 0x00000380	128
# HDA	        0x00000381 ~ 0x000003C0	64
# AUDIO 	    0x000003C1 ~ 0x00000400	64
# GOP(dpu dp)	0x00000401 ~ 0x00000480	128
# NPU	        0x00000481 ~ 0x000004C0	64
# GPU 	      0x000004C1 ~ 0x00000500	64
# VPU	        0x00000501 ~ 0x00000540	64
# ISP	        0x00000541 ~ 0x00000580	64
# Sfh         0x00000581 ~ 0x000005C0	64
# memory	    0x000005C1 ~ 0x00000700	320
# pwr/clk/rst	 0x00000701 ~ 0x00000780	128
# board config 0x00001001 ~ 0x00001100	256
# Setup var    0x00002001 ~ 0x00002100	256
#     	       0x00002101 ~ 0x00002200	256
# MISC0	       0x00002201 ~ 0x00002300	256
# MISC1	       0x00002301 ~ 0x00002400	256

# ACPI	       0x0000A001 ~ 0x0000A200	512
# android 	   0x0000A201 ~ 0x0000A300	256
# linux	       0x0000A301 ~ 0x0000A400	256
# windows	     0x0000A401 ~ 0x0000A500	256
#--------------------------------------------------------------------
